#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn29.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn29.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 29 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 29 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Nāgavagga "
msgstr "1. Dragons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 7. Sutasutta → tassa sutam 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn29.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Sutasutta "
msgstr "7. They’ve Heard "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn29.7:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.7:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.7:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā aṇḍajānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why someone, when their body breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the egg-born dragons?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn29.7:2.1"
msgid "“Idha, bhikkhu, ekacco kāyena dvayakārī hoti, vācāya dvayakārī hoti, manasā dvayakārī hoti. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, it’s when someone does both kinds of deeds by body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "sn29.7:2.2"
msgid "Tassa sutaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "And they’ve heard: "

msgctxt "sn29.7:2.3"
msgid "‘aṇḍajā nāgā dīghāyukā vaṇṇavanto sukhabahulā’ti. "
msgstr "‘The egg-born dragons are long-lived, beautiful, and very happy.’ "

msgctxt "sn29.7:2.4"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "They think: "

msgctxt "sn29.7:2.5"
msgid "‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā aṇḍajānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjeyyan’ti. "
msgstr "‘If only, when my body breaks up, after death, I would be reborn in the company of the egg-born dragons!’ "

msgctxt "sn29.7:2.6"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā aṇḍajānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in the company of the egg-born dragons. "

msgctxt "sn29.7:2.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā aṇḍajānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "This is the cause, this is the reason why someone, when their body breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the egg-born dragons.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn29.7:2.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
